name: holyunblocker
description: Holy Unblocker LTS is a web proxy service that helps you access websites that may be blocked by your network, government or policy all within your browser with no download or setup.

scripts.fresh-install: npm cache verify && npm update && npm ci && cd lib/rammerhead && npm ci
scripts.start: npm stop && npm run build && npm run manual-start
scripts.build: node run-command.mjs build && cd lib/rammerhead && npm run build
scripts.deployment: pnpm install --frozen-lockfile && npm run build && node backend.js
